											Header="Checkable Item Icon"
											InputGestureText="Ctrl+P"
											IsCheckable="True"
											IsChecked="True">
											<MenuItem.Icon>
												<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
											</MenuItem.Icon>
										</MenuItem>
										<MenuItem
											Header="Disabled Checkable Item Icon"
											IsCheckable="True"
											IsChecked="True"
											IsEnabled="False">
											<MenuItem.Icon>
												<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
											</MenuItem.Icon>
										</MenuItem>
									</MenuItem>
									<Separator />
									<MenuItem Header="Save" InputGestureText="Ctrl+S">
										<MenuItem.Icon>
											<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
										</MenuItem.Icon>
									</MenuItem>
									<MenuItem Header="Save As..." InputGestureText="Ctrl+Shift+S" />
									<Separator />
									<MenuItem Header="Disabled Item" IsEnabled="False" />
									<MenuItem
										Header="Checkable Item"
										IsCheckable="True"
										IsChecked="True" />
									<MenuItem
										Header="Disabled Checkable Item"
										IsCheckable="True"
										IsChecked="True"
										IsEnabled="False" />
									<MenuItem
										Header="Checkable Item Icon"
										IsCheckable="True"
										IsChecked="True">
										<MenuItem.Icon>
											<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
										</MenuItem.Icon>
									</MenuItem>
									<MenuItem
										Header="Disabled Checkable Item Icon"
										InputGestureText="Alt+F4"
										IsCheckable="True"
										IsChecked="True"
										IsEnabled="False">
										<MenuItem.Icon>
											<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
										</MenuItem.Icon>
									</MenuItem>
								</MenuItem>
								<MenuItem Header="Edit">
									<MenuItem Header="Undo">
										<MenuItem.Icon>
											<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
										</MenuItem.Icon>
									</MenuItem>
									<MenuItem Header="Redo" />
								</MenuItem>
								<MenuItem Header="No Items" />
								<MenuItem Header="Disabled Item" IsEnabled="False">
									<MenuItem Header="Item 1" />
									<MenuItem Header="Item 2" />
									<MenuItem Header="Item 3" />
								</MenuItem>
							</Menu>
						</Border>
					</StackPanel>

					<StackPanel>
						<StackPanel.Margin>
							<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.JumboThicknessWidth}" />
						</StackPanel.Margin>

						<TextBlock FontSize="{x:Static local:LocalDefaults.LargeFontSize}" Text="ToolBar">
							<TextBlock.Margin>
								<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.MediumThicknessWidth}" />
							</TextBlock.Margin>
						</TextBlock>

						<Border
							Background="{DynamicResource Brush_Background_Low}"
							BorderBrush="{DynamicResource Brush_Border}"
							BorderThickness="1">
							<ToolBarTray
								Width="Auto"
								Margin="10"
								HorizontalAlignment="Left"
								Orientation="Vertical">
								<ToolBar>
									<Button>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</Button>
									<Separator />
									<Button>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</Button>
									<Separator />
									<Button>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</Button>
								</ToolBar>
								<ToolBar Header="Test">
									<ToggleButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</ToggleButton>
									<ToggleButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</ToggleButton>
									<ToggleButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />
									</ToggleButton>
								</ToolBar>
								<ToolBar>
									<xctk:DropDownButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />

										<xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
											<StackPanel>
												<MenuItem Header="Item 1" />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 2" />
												<Separator />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 3" />
											</StackPanel>
										</xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
									</xctk:DropDownButton>
									<xctk:DropDownButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />

										<xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
											<StackPanel>
												<MenuItem Header="Item 1" />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 2" />
												<Separator />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 3" />
											</StackPanel>
										</xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
									</xctk:DropDownButton>
									<xctk:DropDownButton>
										<Image Source="/DarkUI.WPF;component/Resources/search-16.png" />

										<xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
											<StackPanel>
												<MenuItem Header="Item 1" />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 2" />
												<Separator />
												<MenuItem Header="Item 3" />
											</StackPanel>
										</xctk:DropDownButton.DropDownContent>
									</xctk:DropDownButton>
								</ToolBar>
							</ToolBarTray>
						</Border>
					</StackPanel>

					<StackPanel>
						<StackPanel.Margin>
							<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.JumboThicknessWidth}" />
						</StackPanel.Margin>

						<TextBlock FontSize="{x:Static local:LocalDefaults.LargeFontSize}" Text="StatusBar">
							<TextBlock.Margin>
								<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.MediumThicknessWidth}" />
							</TextBlock.Margin>
						</TextBlock>

						<StatusBar>
							<StatusBarItem>Item 1</StatusBarItem>
							<StatusBarItem>Item 2</StatusBarItem>
							<StatusBarItem>Item 3</StatusBarItem>
							<StatusBarItem HorizontalAlignment="Right">
								<StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
									<Button Margin="0,0,5,0">Button</Button>
									<ToggleButton IsChecked="True">Toggle</ToggleButton>
								</StackPanel>
							</StatusBarItem>
						</StatusBar>
					</StackPanel>

					<StackPanel>
						<StackPanel.Margin>
							<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.JumboThicknessWidth}" />
						</StackPanel.Margin>

						<TextBlock FontSize="{x:Static local:LocalDefaults.LargeFontSize}" Text="ProgressBar">
							<TextBlock.Margin>
								<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.MediumThicknessWidth}" />
							</TextBlock.Margin>
						</TextBlock>

						<ProgressBar x:Name="ProgressBar" Value="10" />
					</StackPanel>

					<StackPanel>
						<StackPanel.Margin>
							<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.JumboThicknessWidth}" />
						</StackPanel.Margin>

						<TextBlock FontSize="{x:Static local:LocalDefaults.LargeFontSize}" Text="Slider">
							<TextBlock.Margin>
								<Thickness Bottom="{x:Static darkUI:Defaults.MediumThicknessWidth}" />
							</TextBlock.Margin>
						</TextBlock>

						<Slider Maximum="100" Value="{Binding ElementName=ProgressBar, Path=Value}" />
					</StackPanel>
				</StackPanel>

				<WindowsFormsHost
					x:Name="OriginalPreviewHost"
					Grid.Column="1"
					Margin="15,0,0,0" />
			</Grid>
		</ScrollViewer>
	</Grid>
